text: Radoslav Kasabov (born 30 January 1938) is a Bulgarian wrestler. He competed at the 1960 Summer Olympics and the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1938 births Category:Living people Category:Bulgarian male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Bulgaria Category:Wrestlers at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Wrestlers at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:People from Ruse, Bulgaria
